vue-goodshare

installation.html.title: Installation
installation.html.body:
Installation

Requirements:

Vue.js >= 2.4.0
vue-style-loader >= 3.0.0
css-loader >= 0.28.0
sass-loader >= 6.0.0
node-sass >= 4.6.0


npm
Install component via npm:
$ npm install vue-goodshare --save

Init vue-goodshare component after Vue.js in your main JavaScript file.
There is two way to do this:

Init single share element
Init bundle of share elements
